the RPM file name format should be:
`<name>-<version>-<release>.<architecture>.rpm`
(here http://ftp.rpm.org/max-rpm/ch-rpm-file-format.html or https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rpm_(software)) 

however the current makeDefaultFileName() uses "-" instead of the "." before the architecture.
   ```
private String makeDefaultFileName ()
    {
        final StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder ( RpmLead.toLeadName ( this.name, this.version ) );
        sb.append ( '-' ).append ( this.architecture ).append ( ".rpm" );
        return sb.toString ();
    }
```
